OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,FIt is just after nine in the morning
OL,7,Fand the dusty track hair-pinning its
OL,8,Fway up into the mountains of the Serra
OL,9,FDe Cabrera is deserted.
OL,11,FThe air is heavy with heat, but after
OL,12,Fa week of rain the slopes around us
OL,13,Fare lush and dotted with wildflowers.
OL,15,FHowever, there are tell-tale reminders
OL,16,Fof how fragile this stunning landscape
OL,17,Fis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
