OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,FWe pass a couple of patches burnt out
OL,7,Fin the last year or so, the
OL,8,Fundergrowth beginning to recover, but
OL,9,Fthe trees still blackened stumps.
OL,11,FPortugal has more forest cover than
OL,12,Fany other country in Europe, but has
OL,13,Falso been experiencing record
OL,14,Ftemperatures over the past few years.
OL,16,FIt is a country that still bears the
OL,17,Fscars, both physical and
OL,18,Fpsychological, from its worst disaster
OL,19,Fin decades, back in 2017.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
