OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,FBut we are not searching for cutting-
OL,7,Fedge tech tucked away in these
OL,8,Fplateaus. We are looking for the
OL,9,FGarrano, a breed of semi-wild horses,
OL,10,Fthat until recently were almost as
OL,11,Fendangered as the landscape itself.
OL,13,FWe are with Jose Luite, a retired vet
OL,14,Fwho has spent his life trying to
OL,15,Fprotect the Garrano, after first
OL,16,Friding one as a toddler.
OL,18,FThey have been part of this country's
OL,19,Fheritage since Roman times and there
OL,20,Fwere tens of thousands of them until
OL,21,Fthe late 1990s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
