OL,6,FBut the mechanisation of farms saw
OL,7,Ftheir numbers dwindle until there were
OL,8,Fjust 350 mares left, leaving the
OL,9,FGarrano in danger of disappearing,
OL,10,Funtil now.
OL,12,FTo learn more, we need to find them.
OL,14,FJose thinks the horses will have made
OL,15,Ffor the highest plateaus to try to
OL,16,Fescape the heat, and he's right.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
