OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,FAfter driving for half an hour,
OL,7,Fconstantly scouring the landscape, we
OL,8,Ffinally spot a flash of black, and six
OL,9,For seven Garrano suddenly gallop out
OL,10,Fof the trees.
OL,12,FThey are beautiful; sleek and
OL,13,Fmuscular, their coal-black coats
OL,14,Fglinting in the sunlight. Soon
OL,15,Fadjusting to our presence, they go
OL,16,Fback to munching their way through the
OL,17,Fundergrowth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
