OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,FIt's exactly why they're here. They
OL,7,Fhave been reintroduced into this
OL,8,Flandscape by a project funded by REN -
OL,9,FPortugal's biggest electrical
OL,10,Finfrastructure company.
OL,12,FBetween them, the Garrano can get
OL,13,Fthrough several tonnes of vegetation a
OL,14,Fday, much of it below the giant power
OL,15,Flines that snake their way up from the
OL,16,Fdamn at the bottom of the valley.
OL,18,FPaulo Camacho, REN's head of public
OL,19,Faffairs, has joined us to explain more.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
