OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,FHe tells me: "We have 10,000
OL,7,Fkilometres of lines and 60% of them
OL,8,Fare in forested areas.
OL,10,F"That's the equivalent of thousands of
OL,11,Ffootball pitches of area we have to
OL,12,Fclear every year to stop fires getting
OL,13,Fto the lines and for firefighters to
OL,14,Fget through to fight the fires and to
OL,15,Fprevent the fires going from one side
OL,16,Fto the other."
OL,18,FThe horses don't only graze under the
OL,19,Fpower lines but they help. And
OL,20,FPortugal needs every bit of help it
OL,21,Fcan get.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
