OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,F"When summer arrives we are always
OL,7,Fwaiting to see where the fire is going
OL,8,Fto break," sighs Paulo. "Because it is
OL,9,Fgoing to break, it's always going to
OL,10,Fbreak."
OL,12,FSince the tragedy of 2017, the
OL,13,FPortuguese government has more than
OL,14,Fdoubled its spending on wildfires.
OL,15,FWhile only a fifth of that funding
OL,16,Fused to be spent on prevention, now
OL,17,Fit's nearly half.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
