OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,FOver the course of our week
OL,7,Fcrisscrossing the country, we are
OL,8,Fshown schemes where villages have
OL,9,Fbegun planting new orange trees, less
OL,10,Fflammable than the pine and
OL,11,Feucalyptus, which up until now had
OL,12,Flargely replaced them.
OL,14,FWe are taken to isolated hamlets, like
OL,15,FMos in the Fafe Mountains, to watch
OL,16,Finhabitants taking part in Safe
OL,17,FVillage drills, where firefighters ask
OL,18,Flocals to practise evacuating homes,
OL,19,Fknowing they'll be responsible for
OL,20,Fholding off any fire until the
OL,21,Femergency services can reach them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
