OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,FWe meet helicopter-borne sappers in
OL,7,Fthe north whose job it is to try to
OL,8,Fcontain wildfire ignitions in the
OL,9,Ffirst half an hour after an outbreak
OL,10,Fand visit some of the firefighters.
OL,12,FMany of them are volunteers, stationed
OL,13,Fat potential hot spots over the
OL,14,Fsummer, along with back up crews from
OL,15,Fas far afield as Finland and Latvia -
OL,16,Fpart of the European Union's rescue
OL,17,Fprogramme.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
