OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,FAll of this is coordinated from the
OL,7,FNational Command Centre, just outside
OL,8,FLisbon, where we are shown the award
OL,9,Fwinning technology that gives fire
OL,10,Fchiefs a birds-eye view of what's
OL,11,Fhappening on the ground, along with
OL,12,Fminute by minute predictions of where
OL,13,Ffire may break out or is likely to
OL,14,Fbehave.
OL,16,FAndre Fernandes, a former geography
OL,17,Fspecialist in his forties, leads
OL,18,FPortugal's emergency response and the
OL,19,Fresponsibility of that lies heavily on
OL,20,Fhis shoulders.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
