OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,FWhile preparing to lead National
OL,7,FCommand, he spent two years training
OL,8,Fin firefighting to understand the
OL,9,Fdemands on his crews.
OL,11,FHe tells me that during the summer he
OL,12,Ffinds it hard to sleep, waiting at
OL,13,Fnight for his phone to ring with news
OL,14,Fof another outbreak.
OL,16,F"We will always remember 2017," he
OL,17,Fsays, his face darkening. "That can
OL,18,Fnever happen again. So our daily job,
OL,19,Four focus, our objective is to make
OL,20,Fsure it can't happen again."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
