OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,FHe knows Mother Nature is the
OL,7,Fcruellest of mistresses and can't
OL,8,Fpromise that Portugal is safe.
OL,10,FBut the country's pioneering approach
OL,11,Fseems to be working - despite a
OL,12,Fwarming climate, the number of
OL,13,Fwildfires here has almost halved since
OL,14,F2017.
OL,16,FBut as we fly home, over the dense
OL,17,Fforests of the Iberian Peninsula, it's
OL,18,Fthe reintroduction of the Garrano that
OL,19,Fstays with me.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
