OL,3,CInside Portugal's groundbreaking
OL,4,Cwildfire prevention strategy
OL,6,FIt feels both poetic and practical
OL,7,Fthat Portugal is protecting its
OL,8,Ffuture, against possibly the greatest
OL,9,Fthreat it faces, by embracing the best
OL,10,Fof its past.
OL,12,FYou can watch the latest edition of
OL,13,FITV's On Assignment at 11.30pm tonight
OL,14,Fon ITV1 and ITVX.
